android.car.drivingstate

类 CarDrivingStateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.drivingstate.CarDrivingStateEvent

  • public final class CarDrivingStateEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Driving State related events. Driving State of a car conveys if the car is currently parked, idling or moving.
